leReader/progress_event\"><code>progress</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for File API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileList\"><code>FileList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReaderSync\"><code>FileReaderSync</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/createObjectURL\"><code>URL.createObjectURL()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/revokeObjectURL\"><code>URL.revokeObjectURL()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  The <strong><code>readAsText()</code></strong> method is used to read the contents of the specified <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> or <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a>.\n  When the read operation is complete, the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readyState\" title=\"readyState\"><code>readyState</code></a> is changed to <code>DONE</code>,\n  the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/loadend_event\" title=\"loadend\"><code>loadend</code></a> event is triggered, and the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/result\" title=\"result\"><code>result</code></a> property contains the contents of the file as a text string.\n</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> The <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Blob/text\"><code>Blob.text()</code></a> method is a newer promise-based API to read a file as text.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js-nolint notranslate\">readAsText(blob)\nreadAsText(blob, encoding)\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"blob\"><code>blob</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> or <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a> from which to read.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"encoding\"><code>encoding</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>A string specifying the encoding to use for the returned data. By default, UTF-8 is assumed if this parameter is not specified.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"Return value","isH3":true,"content":"<p>None (<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/undefined\"><code>undefined</code></a>).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>file<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">onchange</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value javascript language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">previewFile</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span cl